title: Do You Expect Bad Things to Happen?
itunes:title: Do You Expect Bad Things to Happen?
description:
When things are going well, do you have a feeling in the back of your head that something bad eventually has to happen? In this episode, I am going to talk about the feeling of "waiting for the other shoe to drop" and how to get past those anxious thoughts so that you can fully experience joy in your life.
